title: HOUR 2- Justin Herbert Oct 27, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 2- Justin Herbert Oct 27, 2020
description:
Justin Herbert tells Dan that he is staying in a hotel because he had to evacuate due to the fires in his area. Justin tells Dan that he only had a minute to adjust and get ready to play when coach told him that he was the starter.
